{"tid":2448947,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"印度封城以來，恒河水達何飲用標準，印度新聞報導","createTime":"2021-03-16T09:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T10:53:25.000Z","uid":168698,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"658f1a9efe588cdbfa7ad47bb653ecefeed66e51","tid":2448947,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2625000/2627389/N14_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2625000%2F2627389%2FN14_1024.jpg&h=bc6514b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.nownews.com/nn_media/thumbnail/2019/12/1577601123-b26afa7ade20be0badd15e3afb697368-696x389.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.nownews.com%2Fnn_media%2Fthumbnail%2F2019%2F12%2F1577601123-b26afa7ade20be0badd15e3afb697368-696x389.jpg&h=ce2d4256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度Zee News報道，印度全國封城近一個月，人類在恆河一帶的活動大減，連帶環境污染問題亦得到改善。原本只適宜洗澡的河水，部分河段水質達到可飲用標準，是自2000年的首次。<br />\n<br />\n有研究指恆河八成污染源頭都是來自人類，河水內含有大量細菌，水質只有B級，只適宜沐浴或其他用途。<br />\n<br />\n印度當局因應新冠病毒疫情，在3月底開始實施全國封城，措施維持至5月初。<br />\n<br />\n封城近一個月後，當局對恆河水質進行檢測。水質樣本來自北阿坎德省，相距約20公里的聖城赫爾德瓦爾及里希蓋什兩處位置，結果發現這個河段水質大為改善。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示河水含氧量增加了20%，意味水底生物有足夠氧氣呼吸，水質亦達到A級標準，即是經過濾後適合飲用，是自2000年以來的首次。"},{"pid":"53423c74e681f1141b650ec5d535bb7fe1f34cdf","tid":2448947,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR4X35wPX-Eplh7zjDZAFAnKrDUK6I8Q1N2zw&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcR4X35wPX-Eplh7zjDZAFAnKrDUK6I8Q1N2zw%26usqp%3DCAU&h=9380813b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64896f145ac302ae94584d0e47174cc5170cd5ee","tid":2448947,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:46